(9, 'Game installation', 'game-installation', '', '<p style="text-align: justify;"> </p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #ff0000;"><strong>Before installing the game please make sure that you have the .NET platform 3.5 installed on your machine. If not you can download it there: </strong></span>[URL="http://www.microsoft.com/downloads/details.aspx?FamilyId=333325FD-AE52-4E35-B531-508D977D32A6&amp;displaylang=en"]here[/URL]</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"> </p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #ff0000;"><strong>In order to play the game you will also need to install Nvidia PhysX on your machine. If you do no have it already you can download it </strong></span>[URL="http://www.nvidia.com/object/physx-9.10.0223-driver.html"]here[/URL]</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"> </p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">There is two ways to install the game on your machine:</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"> </p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Using the installers (recommanded windows XP):</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">[LIST] [*]Download and install the game installer: [URL]http://lbanet.googlecode.com/files/LbanetSetup.msi[/URL] [*]Download and install the images files installer: [URL]http://lbanet.googlecode.com/files/LbanetImageSetup.msi[/URL] [*]Start the game from startup menu or desktop icon <img src="plugins/editors/jce/tiny_mce/plugins/emotions/img/smiley-cool.gif" alt="Cool" title="Cool" border="0" />[/LIST]</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"> </p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Manual installation from archive files (recommanded windows vista and 7):</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">[LIST=1] [*]Download and unpack the game archive: [URL]http://lbanet.googlecode.com/files/LBANet_v0.7.rar[/URL] [*]Run LBANet.exe <img src="plugins/editors/jce/tiny_mce/plugins/emotions/img/smiley-cool.gif" alt="Cool" title="Cool" border="0" />[/LIST]</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"> </p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Game requirements:</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">[LIST] [*]The game has been tested on the following platforms: Windows XP, Windows Vista (32bit and 64bit) and Windows 7 (32bit and 64bit). [*]It was also tested and could run under Mac OSX using Parallels [*]There is no supported linux version for now, but it is planned [*]The game will not run under windows 2000 because IPV6 is not supported there. [*]There is no real minimum requirements, however your graphic card needs to have drivers supporting OpenGL for the game to run correctly. Also your graphic card need to support texture size of at least 2048x2048 [/LIST]</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"> </p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #ff0000;"><strong>Windows 7 and Vista users: the game and game the patcher may need administrator rights to run properly. In order to do it, go in the game directory. Right click on Lbanet.exe. Click on Property in the context menu. Go to the compatibility tab. Check the box "run as administrator". Click the OK button.</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #ff0000;"><strong><br /></strong></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">If you run into trouble installing or playing the game, please post your problem [URL="http://forum.magicball.net/showthread.php?t=14975"]here[/URL]</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Please make sure that you also read the game FAQ before posting <a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=22&amp;Itemid=21">here</a></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">However if you find a bug during gameplay please report it in the bugtracker [URL="http://sacredcarrot.xesf.net/mantis/main_page.php"]here[/URL]</p>', '', 1, 2, 0, 5, '2010-07-02 08:57:51', 62, '', '2010-08-31 15:52:40', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2010-07-02 08:57:51', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=0\nshow_create_date=0\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 33, 0, 9, '', '', 0, 2522, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(11, 'New Release v0.71 + new domain', 'new-release-v071-new-domain', '', '<p><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt; color: #a7fafa;"><img style="float: right;" alt="feather2" src="images/stories/feather2.png" height="150" width="150" /></span></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #a7fafa;">We got a new domain name for  our website, you can now find us at <a href="http://www.lbanet.net/" target="_blank">www.lbanet.net</a></span></p>\r\n<p><br /><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #a7fafa;"> Furthemore we got a new small  release today featuring a new inventory item and a new feature.</span></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p /><span style="font-size: 12pt;" /> \r\n', '</span></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #a7fafa;">Here is a complete list of  the new features:</span></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #a7fafa;">- Added a feather object that allows you to write letters. The writen  letters will appear in the inventory. You can then hide them in  containers if you wish. The feather has been hidden in one of the  containers. So you will first need to find it out ;)</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #a7fafa;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #a7fafa;">- You can now move the shorcut bar on the screen. This way you can  choose the way you want to position all element of the gui on your  screen.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #a7fafa;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #a7fafa;">- Updated game patcher. The patcher will now log its output into a  file named "patching.log". In case of issue during patch please have a  look at this file. The patcher will now also automatically start the  game after it is done.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #a7fafa;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #a7fafa;">- Few bugs fixes.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt; color: #a7fafa;"><br /></span></p>', 1, 2, 0, 1, '2009-11-22 13:54:17', 66, '', '2010-07-05 17:48:11', 66, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2010-07-02 13:53:08', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', '', 13, 0, 12, '', '', 0, 301, ''),
(12, 'New Release v0.75 - NPC actors', 'new-release-v075', '', '<p><img style="float: right;" alt="NPC-small2" src="images/stories/NPC-small2.png" height="150" width="150" /></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; color: #a7fafa;">Here is a new release featuring  the NPC actors. Now the worlds of</span><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; color: #a7fafa;"> Lbanet will be much more lively  that they were before! </span></span></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; color: #a7fafa;">A few new features are also coming with the  NPC.</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; color: #a7fafa;"><br /></span></span></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p /><span style="font-size: 12pt;" /> \r\n', '</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #a7fafa; font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Here is a complete list  of the new features:</span></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #a7fafa; font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">- Added NPC actors. They are  fully animated however they is no real dialog yet. You can already talk  to them but they will not say anything.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #a7fafa; font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #a7fafa; font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">- Added merchants. You can  now buy items from some of the NPC all over the maps.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #a7fafa; font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #a7fafa; font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">- Added actor travel  feature. You should now be able to take use the ferries but also the  cars and motorbikes.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #a7fafa; font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #a7fafa; font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"> - Added scripted zone. Just  try to hide in the trash in the map out of citadel prison ;)</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #a7fafa; font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"><br /></span></p>', 1, 2, 0, 1, '2009-12-06 14:04:55', 66, '', '2010-07-05 17:49:27', 66, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2010-07-02 14:02:30', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', '', 8, 0, 10, '', '', 0, 337, ''),
(13, 'New Release v0.755 - Christmas Event', 'new-release-v0755-christmas-event', '', '<p><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #a7fafa;"><img style="float: right;" alt="christmas" src="images/stories/christmas.png" height="150" width="150" /></span></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #a7fafa;">The LBANet-Team wishes you a  merry merry Christmas! We have got a little surprise for you: </span></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #a7fafa;">"The  LBANet-Christmas-Party-Event"!</span></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;"> \r\n', '</span></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #a7fafa;">Here''s how to join the Party!</span><br /> <br /><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #a7fafa;"> You should now all be ported to the Christmas-Event when you  connect.If you accidently ported out or you have just registered you can  (re-)enter the Christmas-Event either through sendel''s well or by  selecting "Party place" in your teleport-box.</span><br /> <br /> <br /><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #a7fafa;"> The Christmas update features:</span><br /> <br /><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #a7fafa;"> - The Citadel-Island-Party-Scene has been modified for the ultimate  Christmas-event!</span><br /> <br /><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #a7fafa;"> - There are all new Items including e.g. Christmas-Canes, Champagne  and Lebkuchen</span><br /> <br /><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #a7fafa;"> - All the NPCs at the Event-place have got different dialogs that  make sense(!)</span><br /> <br /><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #a7fafa;"> - Santa Clause ! (and other special Christmas-NPCs)</span><br /> <br /><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #a7fafa;"> So, we wish you a merry merry christmas and hope you have fun with  our little Christmas Gift.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt; color: #a7fafa;"><br /></span></p>', 1, 2, 0, 1, '2009-12-24 14:09:07', 66, '', '2010-07-05 17:50:38', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2010-07-02 14:07:07', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 17, 0, 11, '', '', 0, 432, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(14, 'New Release v0.8 - Quests', 'new-release-v08', '', '<p style="color: #a7fafa;"><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt; color: #a7fafa;"><img style="float: right;" alt="Quests-small" src="images/stories/Quests-small.png" height="150" width="150" /></span></p>\r\n<p style="color: #a7fafa;"> </p>\r\n<p style="color: #a7fafa;"><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #a7fafa;">This was a long waiting, but finally the new release is up and  running featuring dialogs and quests!</span></p>\r\n<p style="color: #a7fafa;"><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #a7fafa;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p /><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;" /> \r\n', '</span></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #a7fafa;">Here is the release  content:</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #a7fafa;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #a7fafa;">- added dialog mechanism.  Now NPC can have extended conditionnnal dialog trees.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #a7fafa;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #a7fafa;">- added quest feature.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #a7fafa;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #a7fafa;">- added journal in game  (parchment icon)</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #a7fafa;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #a7fafa;">- 2 quests have been added  in LbaxExpanded world for testing purpose.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #a7fafa;">The first one is given by  Baldino. For the second one just go have a look at Principal Island  stables ;)</span></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #a7fafa;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt; color: #a7fafa;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">There is only thosetwo  quests for now, but all mechanisms are in place. So now we can easily  populate the world with extensive dialogs and a buch of quest</span> <img src="plugins/editors/jce/tiny_mce/plugins/emotions/img/smiley-tongue-out.gif" alt="Tongue out" title="Tongue out" border="0" /></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt; color: #a7fafa;"><br /></span></p>', 1, 2, 0, 1, '2010-02-21 14:13:58', 66, '', '2010-07-05 17:49:09', 66, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2010-07-02 14:12:36', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', '', 12, 0, 7, '', '', 0, 487, ''),
(15, 'New Release v0.9 + Lbanet is 1 year old', 'new-release-v09-lbanet-is-1-year-old', '', '<p><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt; color: #a7fafa;"><img style="float: right;" alt="birthday-small" src="images/stories/birthday-small.png" height="150" width="150" /><span style="font-size: 12pt;"> </span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt; color: #a7fafa;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Today we have 2 good news for  you:</span></span></p>\r\n<p><br /><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #a7fafa;"> - Lbanet is turning 1 year old! Yes it is already 1 year that the first version of  the game was released on MBN. </span><br /> <br /><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #a7fafa;"> - To celebrate this great  event we have a new release v0.9 featuring a lot of new stuf...</span></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p /><span style="font-size: 12pt;" /> \r\n', '\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #a7fafa;">Lbanet has turned 1 year old.  Yes it is 1 year that the first version of the game was released on MBN. </span><br /> <br /><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #a7fafa;"> A lot of things have changed since then already and there is still a  lot to do for the future. I just hope that </span><br /><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #a7fafa;"> so far you enjoyed  playing as much as I enjoyed making this game!</span><br /> <br /><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #a7fafa;"> So in order to celebrate we have a new release v0.9 featuring a lot  of new stuff:</span><br /> <br /><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #a7fafa;"> - new physic engine base on Nvidia PhysX</span><br /><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #a7fafa;"> - the magic ball has  been added</span><br /><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #a7fafa;"> - the magic ball can activate switches</span><br /><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #a7fafa;"> -  implementation of the pvp in game. Collecting pvp statistics to display  on the website <a href="http://lbanet.net/index.php?idcatside=8">here </a>(number  of kill, death, ...)</span><br /> <br /> <br /><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #a7fafa;"> In order to play the game you will need to install nvidia PhysX on  your machine if you do no have it already, you can download it here: <a target="_blank" href="http://www.nvidia.com/object/physx-9.10.0223-driver.html">http://www.nvidia.com/object/physx-9.10.0223-driver.html</a></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #a7fafa;"><br /></span></p>', 1, 2, 0, 1, '2010-06-30 14:17:44', 66, '', '2010-08-05 09:39:00', 66, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2010-07-02 14:15:51', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 17, 0, 8, '', '', 0, 809, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(16, 'Best Pvp players:', 'best-pvp-players', '', '{source}<span style="font-family: courier new, courier, monospace;"><br /><br />[[?php<br />$i = 0;<br />$abfrage = "SELECT </span>jos_users.id as uid, <span style="font-family: courier new, courier, monospace;">jos_users.username</span> as uname<span style="font-family: courier new, courier, monospace;">, SUM(lba_usertoworld.PvpKill) as pkill, SUM(lba_usertoworld.PvpDeath) as pdeath from </span>jos_users, <span style="font-family: courier new, courier, monospace;">lba_users, lba_usertoworld where </span>jos_users.id = lba_users.josiid AND <span style="font-family: courier new, courier, monospace;">lba_users.id = lba_usertoworld.userid GROUP BY lba_usertoworld.userid ORDER BY SUM(lba_usertoworld.PvpKill) DESC, SUM(lba_usertoworld.PvpDeath) ASC, </span>jos_users.<span style="font-family: courier new, courier, monospace;">username ASC LIMIT 0,50";<br />$ergebnis = mysql_query($abfrage) or die(mysql_error().''<span>&lt;</span>hr /<span>&gt;</span>''.$abfrage.''<span>&lt;</span>hr /<span>&gt;</span>'');<br />echo "<span>&lt;</span>table style=\\"width: 600px;\\"<span>&gt;</span><span>&lt;</span>tr<span>&gt;</span><span>&lt;</span>td<span>&gt;</span>Rank:<span>&lt;</span>/td<span>&gt;</span><span>&lt;</span>td<span>&gt;</span>Username:<span>&lt;</span>/td<span>&gt;</span><span>&lt;</span>td<span>&gt;</span>PVP-Kills:<span>&lt;</span>/td<span>&gt;</span><span>&lt;</span>td<span>&gt;</span>PVP-Deaths:<span>&lt;</span>/td<span>&gt;</span><span>&lt;</span>/tr<span>&gt;</span>";<br />while($row = mysql_fetch_object($ergebnis))<br /><img src="plugins/editors-xtd/sourcerer/images/tab.png" alt="&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;" />{<br /><img src="plugins/editors-xtd/sourcerer/images/tab.png" alt="&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;" />$i = $i+1;<br /><img src="plugins/editors-xtd/sourcerer/images/tab.png" alt="&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;" />echo "<span>&lt;</span>tr<span>&gt;</span>";<br /><img src="plugins/editors-xtd/sourcerer/images/tab.png" alt="