(22, 'FAQ', 'faq', '', '<p style="text-align: justify;"> </p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><b>Do I need to pay something to play the game?<br /> </b>The game is free to play. However you should keep in mind that this game is a modification of the original game Little Big Adventure. So you need to own a copy of the  original LBA1 and LBA2 games in order to be allowed to play this game.<br /> <b><br /> <br /> The game just crashes after installation, it does not even start:<br /> </b>First make sure that you have the .NET platform 3.5 installed on  your machine, you can find it <a target="_blank" href="http://www.microsoft.com/downloads/details.aspx?FamilyId=333325FD-AE52-4E35-B531-508D977D32A6&amp;displaylang=en">here</a>.<br /> Also make sure that the visual C++ 2008 redistribuable is also  installed, you can find it <a target="_blank" href="http://www.microsoft.com/downloads/details.aspx?FamilyID=9b2da534-3e03-4391-8a4d-074b9f2bc1bf&amp;displaylang=en">here</a>.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">In order to play the  game you will also need to install nvidia PhysX on your machine if you  do no have it already, you can download it <a target="_blank" href="http://www.nvidia.com/object/physx-9.10.0223-driver.html">here</a></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Finally make sure you have correctly followed the <a target="_self" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=9:game-installation&amp;catid=5&amp;Itemid=11">installation instructions</a> and  check wether your operating system is supported, for example the game will not run over windows 2000.<br /> <br /> <b> <br /> I can not connect to the game server, an error message tells me "Server  version mismatch - please update your game"</b>:<br /> You do not have the latest version of the client, please update your  game using the game patcher.<br /> <br /> <br /> <br /> <b>I can start the game and run it but the game is really slow:</b><br /> It often come from the fact that your video card driver does not support  OpenGL correctly. <br /> Please make sure that you install the latest driver from your card  manufacturer and not from windows.<br /> <br /> <br /> <br /> <b>When I connect to a map I can see twinsen but the rest is blank or  look like this: </b><br /> <img alt="eek1" src="images/stories/eek1.jpg" height="113" width="153" /><br /> You did not install the bricks images files, please check the <a target="_self" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=9:game-installation&amp;catid=5&amp;Itemid=11"> installation instruction</a> there to see how to do it.<br /> <br /> <br /> <b>The game patcher does not seem to work properly, I can not get  updates:<br /> </b>First check the patching.log file created in the lbanet.exe to see  if you get an error message there. Then make sure that your firewall  does not block LBANet.exe. If so please add LBANet.exe but also  patchingclient.exe to your firewall allowed list.<br /> <br /> <br /> <b>The map looks horrible, there is a lot of glitches or holes in there!</b><br /> This is due to the fact that we build a real 3D view out of 2D sprites.  So we get a perspective view but then we also get a lot of glitches. <br /> This is a trade off so if you really do not like how the game looks, you  can reset the view to isometric under the game option.<br /> <br /> <br /> <b>I found a bug! What shall I do? Is this game of so poor  quality?</b><br /> Keep in mind that the game is made by a very small team. Do not expect  to get a professionnal game from today to tomorrow. <br /> We are constantly in the proccess to update and clean game content. So  if you find a bug please post it here:<a href="http://sacredcarrot.xesf.net/mantis/main_page.php" target="_blank"> </a><a href="http://sacredcarrot.xesf.net/mantis/main_page.php" target="_blank">http://sacredcarrot.xesf.net/mantis/main_page.php</a>. We will then try  to solve it asap.<br /> <br /> <br /> <strong>I like the game and I would like to help, what can I do?</strong><br /> All the help is accepted as long as you are motivated. Here is a list of  some possible tasks to be done:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Game testing (try to find glitches in the game and  report them in the bugtracker).</li>\r\n<li>Creating a short video trailer of the game.</li>\r\n<li>Creating some new worlds for the game, now all the tools are  available so just try them out!</li>\r\n<li>Porting and maintaining LBANet over Linux</li>\r\n<li>Porting and maintaining LBANet over Mac OSX</li>\r\n<li>If you are a C++ programmer, we are looking for someone to port the  game under OpenSG engine</li>\r\n<li>Create stories and dialogs for LBANet</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>In any case, just send me a PM (user Rincevent), then we can discuss together about  how you would help the best.</p>', '', 1, 2, 0, 5, '2010-07-05 15:11:37', 62, '', '2010-08-31 15:54:40', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2010-07-05 15:11:37', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=0\nshow_modify_date=0\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 19, 0, 6, '', '', 0, 729, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(23, 'Screenshots', 'screenshots', '', '<p>{phocagallery view=category|categoryid=1|limitstart=0|limitcount=40|imageshadow=none|detail=3|displayname=0|displaydetail=0|displaydownload=0|displaybuttons=0|displaydescription=0|displayimgrating=0|bgcolor=transparent|imagebgcolor=transparent|bgcolorhover=transparent|bordercolor=#A7FAFA|bordercolorhover=#FFAAAA}</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>If you have nice screenshots of the game and wish to see them published here, send a PM to <a href="index.php?option=com_comprofiler&amp;Itemid=3">Rincevent</a>.</p>', '', 1, 2, 0, 5, '2010-07-05 15:11:54', 62, '', '2010-08-31 15:49:39', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2010-07-05 15:11:54', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=0\nshow_modify_date=0\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 23, 0, 5, '', '', 0, 1266, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(24, 'Gameplay videos', 'gameplay-videos', '', '<p> </p>\r\n<p>Introduction:</p>\r\n<p>http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=N0SpOJPugjc</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>General video:</p>\r\n<p>http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KsUNKX5LYfo</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>All Outfit And Color Options:</p>\r\n<p>http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LvtRHMKdeC8</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>Interactions:</p>\r\n<p>http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qmPVVtlRUhU</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>Testing The Protopack:</p>\r\n<p>http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=byakPtiWO2E</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>Museum Visit:</p>\r\n<p>http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yJN2wEbbhms</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>Dino-Fly:</p>\r\n<p>http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=elmKk5q65Ls</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>Magic ball and Pvp:</p>\r\n<p>http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3U2b_ry53U0</p>', '', 1, 2, 0, 5, '2010-07-05 15:12:14', 62, '', '2010-08-31 15:47:59', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2010-07-05 15:12:14', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=0\nshow_modify_date=0\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 13, 0, 4, '', '', 0, 1134, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(25, 'Credits', 'credits', '', '<p> </p>\r\n<p><b>The current team is composed by:</b></p>\r\n<blockquote>Vivien Delage (Rincevent_123):  Project lead an game progammer<br /></blockquote>\r\n<blockquote><br /></blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>Kobold: Test lead and map modder<br /> <br /> leoboe: Game 2D designer, website designer, map modder</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote><br /> Link: Server provider, administration and maintenance<br /></blockquote>\r\n<blockquote><br /></blockquote>\r\n<blockquote><br /></blockquote>\r\n<p><b>Contributors:<br /> </b></p>\r\n<blockquote>Polaris: Designed a few maps for the game like one house  in Old Burg and a room in Tippet island.<br /> <br /> Homeless: Created the base image for the current lbanet logo.</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote><br /></blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>Fanlba: French translator</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote><br /></blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>mazaka151: Created the gameplay videos.<br /></blockquote>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><b><br /> Special thanks:<br /> </b></p>\r\n<blockquote>To Adeline software for creating the original LBA games.  They are the reason why we are there today.</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote><br /></blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>To David38 whose perspective map viewer, based  on RobG concept, was of a great help in order to build my own game  engine. <br /> <br /> To Alexfont and his LBAnimator that was also essential for the character  animation part of my engine.<br /> <br /> To elmuerte for creating MBN which is really a great forum.<br /> To .TaKaM for his nice smileys <img src="plugins/editors/jce/tiny_mce/plugins/emotions/img/smiley-cool.gif" alt="Cool" title="Cool" border="0" /><br /> <br /> To all of you guys, members of  the great Magicball network community,  for the cheer up and support.<br /> <br /> <br /> <br /> <br /></blockquote>\r\n<p>If you are interested in joining the team and helping the  game please send me a PM, there is always room for motivated people  wanting to help! We are actively looking for people being able to port and maintain  Lbanet over Linux and Mac OSX</p>', '', 1, 2, 0, 5, '2010-07-05 17:59:32', 62, '', '2010-07-28 17:42:01', 66, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2010-07-05 17:59:32', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=0\nshow_modify_date=0\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 11, 0, 1, '', '', 0, 598, 'robots=\nauthor='),
