(43, 'Incredible', 'incredible', '', 'Whoa! This is awesome. Then... with the new engine, are we going to be able to create new LBA2 islands, and incorporate then into a LBANet world without needing any "LBA2 Island Creator" or something like that? Really? This is my dream made true...  :lol: I can''t wait for it.', '', 1, 3, 0, 3, '2010-10-15 14:23:42', 546, 'Sara', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', '', 1, 39, 1, '', '', 0, 0, ''),
